{"tid":2109513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富東閣出Post 要求01 同衛生署澄清確診者能否確診後才光顧","createTime":"2020-07-15T09:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T08:55:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f541887982bfa25ce7501e6122984cbdc88dda92","tid":2109513,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"請求還我清白<br />\n<br />\n要求澄清啟事。7月14日零晨，HK01首發佈有新冠肺炎確診者曾到過本店。本店十分質疑該報道。亦因此報道，其他傳媒，以及衞生處亦將本店列入確診者曾到過的地方名單中。<br />\n<br />\n確診者1434，<br />\n2020年7月8日發病，<br />\n2020年7月12日報告，<br />\n但2020年7月13日到本店？<br />\n<br />\n確診者1372，<br />\n無病徵，<br />\n2020年7月10日報告<br />\n但2020年7月13日到本店？<br />\n<br />\n兩名事主於確診後才到本店？詭異，無理由，亦不可能吧！一經確診還能四處走動？不是已被要求入院了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n以下圖片及網站連結供參考<br />\n<br />\n衞生處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2Flocal_situation_covid19_tc.pdf&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=a44a916a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/files/pdf/local_situation_covid19_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\nHK01 新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/497549?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F497549%3Futm_source%3D01appshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=276426d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/497549?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/320199598676608/posts/560607507969148/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F320199598676608%2Fposts%2F560607507969148%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=aa39bd64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/320199598676608/posts/560607507969148/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3